            <h1>Children and youth</h1>
            <div class="temaMobIngressImg" style="display: none;"><img src="/Upload/BLD/Temabilder/Hovedtemabilder/Barn_og_ungdom_Tema_150x113.jpg" alt="Barn og ungdom
Barn og ungdom" /></div>
            <p class="textIngress">The Ministry of Children and Equality is responsible for multi-sectoral policies directed toward children and youth.
</p>
            <img src="/Upload/BLD/Temabilder/Hovedtemabilder/Barn_og_ungdom_Tema_150x113.jpg" alt="Barn og ungdom
Barn og ungdom" class="temaIngressImg" />
            <div class="descriptionText"><p>And overarching goal of Norway's child and youth policies is to secure a good, safe environment in which children and young people can to grow to adulthood. Services and opportunities are to be equal for everyone. Of central importance are efforts to combat marginalization, equalize living standards and promote opportunities for children and young people to influence social developments. Such efforts are undertaken in concert with other ministeries, national agencies, municipalities and non-governmental organizations.<br /></p></div>
