        <div class="ArticleView"> 
            
            <div class="ArticleContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/kd/Selected-topics/gender-equality-/gender-equality-in-kindergartens.html?id=552008" title="">
                        Gender Equality in Kindergartens
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Editorial article, Ministry of Education and Research, 31.03.2009]</p>
                <p>From 1 January 2006, day care centres come under the Ministry of Education and Research, rather than the Ministry of Children and Equality. This means that day care centres in Norway are regarded as being part of the educational system, part of the learning process.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
