                        Summary of Report No. 16 (2006-2007) to the Storting
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Guidelines and brochures, Ministry of Education and Research, 05.02.2008]</p>
                <p>Summary of Report No. 16 (2006-2007) to the Storting, the Norwegian Government’s white paper on early intervention for lifelong learning.</p>
                
                
